from csaps import csaps

def interp_TS_dat_simple(R,Te,Ne,LCFS,R_0,sm_fac):
    #sm_fac = 0.9
    iR = np.arange(R_0, LCFS, 0.0025)
    iTe = csaps(R, Te, smooth=sm_fac)
    iTe = iTe(iR)
    iNe = csaps(R, Ne, smooth=sm_fac)
    iNe = iNe(iR)
    iR_n = [((i-R_0)/(LCFS-R_0)) for i in iR]
    return iR_n, iTe, iNe
